window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The roll of the dice,<br> The flip of the cards,<br> I love it all.<br> The risk,<br> The chance,<br> The odds.</p> <p>Which is why I'm here again,<br> In over my head,<br> Drowning in debt,<br> With no clear way out.</p> <p>But when a sexy, commanding boss makes me an offer.<br> I can't refuse.<br> After all,<br> It can't be that hard being married to the Brash Boss.</p> <p>But deals struck over money should never involve the heart... </p>"; 
